    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions like @Compendium[pf1.spells.c1e7f0ct04k270wy]{create undead}, except that you can create more powerful and intelligent sorts of undead: shadows, wraiths, spectres, and devourers. The type or types of undead created is based on caster level, as shown below.</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Caster Level</th>\n<th>Undead Created</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>15th or lower</td>\n<td>Shadow</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>16th-17th</td>\n<td>Wraith</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>18th-19th</td>\n<td>Spectre</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>20th or higher</td>\n<td>Devourer</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
